dataIdInfo.idAbs: This polygon data layer represents right of ways for Green County, Wisconsin in 2012. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Green_Roads_2012.gdb.[Features were derived from a variety of sources including deeds, descriptions, subdivision maps, certified survey maps, easements, and right of way maps. These source materials were of varying scale and date. This coverage provides a representation of the geometry and topology of tax parcels within the County, and is suitable as a reference layer within the County's GIS.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This layer is intended for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[This layer is intended as a base layer for use with other digital data developed by agencies within Green County.]
